  '\n\nO give thanks unto the lord, for his coming\nBass: For his coming\nO give thanks unto the lord, for his coming\nBass: For his coming\nFor his mercy endureth forever forever\nSoprano, alto, ten: Sing unto the lord\nBass: All ye earth\nSoprano, alto, ten: Sing unto the lord\nBass: All ye earth\nAll: Sing unto the lord, sing unto the lord.\nSing praise unto the lord.\nBass: Praise ye the lord\nAll: Praise the lord, praise the lord\nLet everything that hath breath, praise the lord\nO let us praise him, o let us praise him\nLet everything that hath breath praise the lord.\n\nChorus:\nRejoice, rejoice for our king\nRejoice, rejoice for our king.\nOur king has taken his right place\nGod has sent him over the nation.\n\n',
