  '\n\n1. Vuyani ngamaxesha onke\nNgumyalelo wenkosi yam\n\n2. Thandazani ningayeki\nNgumyalelo wenkosi yam\n\n3. Ningacimi umoya\nNgumyalelo wenkosi\n\n4. Ningadeli iziprofitesho\nNgumyalelo wenkosi yam.\n\n5. uYesu wafela mna nawe\nEntabeni ye-Calvary\n\n6. uYesu walilela mna nawe\nEntabeni ye-Calvary\n\n7. Bazalwana sithandazeleni\nNgumyalelo wenkosi yam.\n\n',
  '\n\nSirayeli vuyani,\nSirayeli vuyani\nSirayeli vuyani,\nEmoyeni wesiprofitesho.\n\n',
  '\n\nNina ndlu ka-Yakobi\nYizani masihambe\nSiye ekukhayeni\nKuka-Yehova.\n\n',
