  "\n\nKwakuya kuthi emihleni yokuphela\nKwakuya kuthi emihleni yokuphela\nIntaba yendlu ka Yehova\nYophakanyiselwa phezu kwenduli\nZithi zonk' izizwe zele kuyo\nZithi zonk' izizwe zele kuyo\nZithi masiye endlwini ka Thixo.\n\nChorus:\nKuya kuphuma umthetho eZion\nKuya kuphuma umthetho eZion\nKuya kuphuma umthetho eZion\nNelizwi lika Yehova eYerusalem.\n\n",
  "\n\n1. Ukuba akuthethi njengengelosi\nUkuba akushumayeli njengo Paulusi\nUnga'uxelutando luka-Yesu.\n\nChorus:\nKwelothunzi lelo liwa\nKwelothunzi lelo liwa\nKamsinyane ndiyakuphumla\nKwelothunzi lelo liwa.\n\n2. Ukuba awungebi ngumalusi\nOmi phezu kwendonga zeZion\nUsalatindlela eya ezulwini\nUnike'uxolo kubo bonke.\n\n3. Ukuba awungesi\nElizweni laba\nUngabafumana aba bekufuphi\nUngabanceda elucangweni labo\n\n",
