  "1. II Timote 3:16 zonke izibhalo zinikwa ngokuphefumlelwa kukaTixo zinceda kanjalo ukuba kufundiswe, ukuba kohlwaywe, ukuba kulungiswe, ukuba kululekwe ebulungiseni. 2. mateyu 5:17 ningabi ndeza ukutshabalalisa umteto umhlaumbi abaprofite, andizanga ukutshabalalisa koko ndize ukuzafisekisa. 3. luke 13:33 kodwa ndifanele ukuti namhla nangomso nangomso omnye ndihambe, ngokuba kungebe njalo ukuba umprofite abubele ngapandle kweYerusalem. 4. II petrosi 1:21 ngokuba kungezanga kuziswe isiprofitesho ngentando yomntu koko abantu abangcwele bakaTixo batetayo bequtywa ngumoya oyingcwele. 5. hamosi 3:7 ngenyaniso ayiyi kwenza nto inkosi enguYehova ukuba ayityilanga iqinga layo kwizicaka zayo abaprofite. 6. II zikronike 20:20 baza bavuka kusasa ngomnye umhla bapuma ukuya entlango yasetekoha, nasekupumeni kwabo wema uyehoshefate wati, ndipulapuleni bojuda nabemi baseyerusalem, kolwani kuYehova uTixo wenu naniya kuqiniswa, kolwani kubaprofite bake naniya kutamsanqeleka. 7. imibalo 12:6 wayesiti: yivani ke amazwi am ukuba kubako umprofite pakati kwenu, mna yehova ndiya kuzazisa ngomboniso kuye, ngepupa ndiya kuteta naye. 8. jeremiya 1:5 ndingekakudali esiswini bendikwazi, kwa ungekapumi esizalweni ndakwahlula ndakumisela ube ngumprofite ezizweni. 9. zekariya 7:7 la mazwi asingawo na awawashumayelayo uYehova ngabaprofite bapambili, okuya iYerusalem ibimiwa, nokuya ibinokonwaba nezixeko zayo eziyingqongayo, kwakumiwa iswide netafa. 10. joweli 2:23 kwakuya kuti emva koko ndogalela umoya wam pezu koluntu lonke, babeya kuprofitesha onyana benu nentombi zenu, amaxego enu ayakupupa amapupa, amadodana enu ayakubona imiboniso. 11. I korinte 14:22 kwanjalo ke ezinye inteto azingumqondiso kwabo bakolwayo, zinguwo kwabangakoliweyo. kodwa isiprofitesho asiyinto yabangakoliweyo siyinto yabakolwayo. 12. ma-efese 4:11-13 waza yena ngokwake wanika abanye babe ngabapostile, nabanye babe ngabaprofite, nabanye babe ngabavangeli, nabanye babengabelusi nabefundisi. 12. kuze kuzalisekiswe abangcwele ngenxa yomsebenzi wobukonzi, ngenxa yokwakiwa komzimba kakristu. 13. side siti tina sonke sifikelele kubunye bokolo nobokwaziwa konyana kaTixo, kwindoda ekulileyo, kumlinganiso wobude bobuzala bukakristu. 13. I makorinte 12:28 kanjako abanye uTixo ubabakile erementeni, ngokokuqala abapostile, ngokwesibini abaprofite, ngokwesitatu abefundisi, emva koko imimangaliso, kamva izipiwo zokupilisa, intsizo, impato, intlobo ngentlobo zenteto. 14. zenzo zabapostile 21:18-11 kekaloku nxa sibe silibala kona imihla yamininzi, kwehla ejudeya umprofite otile ogama lalingu-agabusi. 11. weza ke kuti watabata umbinqo kapaulos wabopa ezake izandla nenyawo wati, utsho umoya oyingcwele ukuti londoda umbinqo lo ungowayo amajuda ayakwenjenjalo ukuyibopa eyerusalem, ayeya kuyinikela ezandleni zabahedeni. 15. I makorinte 13:9-10 ngokuba sisazi ngokwenxenye kanjalo siprofitesha ngokwenxenye. 10. kodwa xeshekweni kufika oko kufezekileyo kuya kwandula oko kungokwenxenye kutshabalale. 16. I matesalonika 5:20 ningadeli iziprofrtesho. 17. sityilo sikajohane 19:10 ndaza ndawa pambi kwenyawo zayo ukuba ndiyibedeshe yayisiti kum: lumka ungenjenjalo, ndisisicaka kunye nawe, nakunye nabazalwana bako abanabo ubungqina bukayesu, mbedeshe uTixo ngokuba ubungqina buka-Yesu bungumoya wobuprofitesho. 18. isityilo sika-johane 12:17 yaza yaqumba inamba leyo ngakuyo lo nkazana yapuma ukuya kwenza imfazwe nabaseleyo benzalo yayo, abayigcinayo imiyafelo katixo, abanabo ubungqina bukayesu kanjalo.",
  "1.  genesis 2.  ikesodus 3.  ilevitikus 4.  imibalo 5.  iduteronomi 6.  uyoshuvva 7.  abagwebi 8.  urute 9.  eyokuqala ka-samyali 10. eyesibini ka-samyali 11. eyokuqala yokumkani 12. eyesibini yokumkani 13. eyokuqala yezikronike 14. eyesibini yezikronike 15. u-ezera 16, unehemiya 17. u-estere 18. u-jobi 19. amaculo 20. imizekeliso 21. umshumayeli 22. ingoma ka-solomoni 23. uyisaya 24. u-jeremiya 25. izililo 26. u-hezekile 27. u-danyeli 28. u-hosheha 29. u-joweli 30. u-hamosi 31. u-hobadiya 32. u-jona 33. u-mika 34. u-nahume 35. uhabakuke 36. u-tsefaniya 37. u-hagai 38. u-zekariya 39. u-malaki",
  "1.  ivangeli ka-mateyu 2.  ivangeli ka-maraki 3.  ivangeli ka-luke 4.  ivangeli ka-johane 5.  izenzo zabapostile 6.  incwadi ka-paulusi kumaroma 7.  eyokuqala incwadi ka-paulusi kuma-korinte 8.  eyesibini incwadi ka-paulusi kuma-korinke 9.  incwadi ka-paulusi kuma-galati 10. incwadi ka-paulusi kuma-efese 11. incwadi ka-paulusi kumafilipu 12. incwadi ka-paulusi kumakolose 13. eyokuqala incwadi ka-paulus kumatesalonika 14. eyesibini incwadi ka-paulus kumatesalonika 15. eyokuqala incwadi ka-paulusi ku-timote 16. eyesibini incwadi ka-paulus ku-timote 17. incwadi ka-paulusi ku-titusi 18. incwadi ka-paulusi ku-filemoni 19. incwadi ka-paulusi kuma-hebere 20. incwadi ka-yakobi 21. eyokuqala incwadi ka-petrosi 22. eyesibini incwadi ka-petrosi 23. eyokuqala incwadi ka-johane 24. eyesibini incwadi ka-johane 25. eyesithathu incwadi ka-johane 26. incwadi ka-juda 27. isityilo sika-johane",
  "1. I Makorinte 1:10 kekaloku ndiyanikunga bazalwane ngalo igama lenkosi yetu uyesu kristu ukuba nibe nokuteta okukwakunye nonke, ize zingabiko impambano pakati kwenu, kodwa nibe nizalisekile kolukwalunye uluvo nakwekwanye ingcingo. 2. mateyu 11:23-29 yizani kum nonke nina nidiniweyo nitwesiwe kakulu ndandiya kuti mna ndinipumze. 2. twalani iyokwe yam pezu kwenu nifunde ngam ngokuba ndilulamile ndinentliziyo ethobekileyo, naniya kufumanela imipefumlo yenu ukupumla. 3. ivangeli ka-johane 13:34 -35 umyalelo omtsha ndiyawunika kuni ukuba nitandane njengokuba nditandile nina ukuba nani nitandane kwanjalo. 35. ngako oku bayakukwazi bonke ukuba ningabadisipile bam ukuba ninotando omnye komnye. 4. magalati 5:1 qinisani ukuma ngoko kulo nkulufeko usenzile sikululekile ngayo ukristu nize ningabuyi nibanjelwe eyokweni yobukoboka. 5. maroma 8:38-39 ngokuba ndikoliwe ukuba kwa nokufa, nobom, nengelosi, nabanegunya, nabanamandla, nezinto ezikoyo, nezinto eziza kubako. 39. nobude, nobunzulu, nesinye isidalwa esisimbi, aziyi kubanako ukuba zingasahlula elutandweni luka-Tixo, olukuye u-kristu yesu inkosi yetu. 6. imizekeliso 18:10 gama likayehova liyinqaba yamandla, olungileyo uyabalekela kuyo anqabe ke. 7. isityilo sika-johane 22:14 banetamsanqa abayenzayo imiyalelo yake, ukuze babe negunya pezu kwawo umti wobom, baze bati ngamasango aso, bangene esixekweni. 8. ivangeli ka-johane 8:31-32 wabesiti ngoko uyesu kuma-juda lawo abekolwa nguye, xeshekweni nihlala elizwini lam ningabadisipile bam ngenyaniso. 32. naniya kuyazi inyaniso, iti yona inyaniso inikululekise. 9. mafilipu 3:14 ndiyaputuma ke ngakuwo umlinganiso ndiputumela umvuzo wobizo lwapezulu luka-tixo ku-kristu yesu. 10. maroma 1:16 ngokuba ndingenantloni ngayo ivangeli ka-kristu, ngokuba ingamandla ka-Tixo ibe lusindiswa kubo bonke abakolwayo, kwakuye umjuda ukuqala, nakuye umgrike. 11. mahebere 12:1-2 ngako oko ke nati sinesihiwele esikulu kangaka samangqina sisipahla nje masibeke nxamnye imitwalo yonke, naso isono esirawulayo kakuhle siti ngomonde sibaleke ugqatso esilubekelwayo. 2. sikangela ngakuye oyimbangi nomfezekisi wokolo lwetu uyesu, owati ngenxa yovuyo olube lubekwa pambi kwake wayinyamezela ikurusi, elidelile ihlazo nje, waza wahlala pantsi ngasekunene kweterone ka-tixo. 12. umpostile u-johane I 5:2-3 ngako oku siyazi ukuba siyalutanda usapo luka-Tixo okuya uTixo simtandayo nemiyalelo yake siyigcinayo. 3. ngokuba lulo olu utando luka-Tixo ukuba siyigcine imiyalelo yake, imiyalelo yake ayinzima ke. 13. maroma 8:1 ngako kaloku akuko kugwetywa kwabo bakuye u-kristu yesu abati bangahambi ngokwenyama koko bahambe ngokomoya.",
  "1. yisaya 58:13 ukuba uyanqanda unyawo lwako kuyo isabata ungenzi eyako intando ngawo umhla wam oyingcwele, ukuba uyabiza isabata ngokuti sisiyolo, umhla oyingcwele kaYehova ngokuti ubekekile, uze uwubeke, ungenzi ezako indlela, ungafuni eyako intando, ungateti awako amazwi. 2. jeremeya 17:27 kodwa nxa ningayi kundipulapula ukuba niwenze ngcwele umhla wesabata nokuba ningatwali namnye umtwalo, koko niyakungena ngamasango eYerusalem ngomhla wesabata, ndiyakwandula ndipembe umililo emasangweni ayo, oyakuzidla ingxande zaseYerusalem ungacinywa. 3. jeremiya 17:22 kanjalo ningapuni nomtwalo ezindlwini zenu ngomhla wesabata ningenzi namnye umsebenzi, koko niyakuwenza ngcwele umhla wesabata njengokuba bendiyalela oyihlo benu. 4. kesodus 35:3 aniyi kupemba mlilo kuzo zonke izindlu zenu ngomhla wesabata. 5. kesodus 16:22-29 kwaza kwati ngemini yesitandatu babuta isonka esiphindiweyo zazizi-omere zimbini kumntu mnye, zasuka inkosana zentlanganiso zeza zaxela kuMosese. 23. wayesiti kuzo: koku u-Yehova akutshilo ngomso lixesha lopumlo, isabata eyingcwele kuYehova, leyo niya kuyoja yojeni naleyo niyakuyipeka yipekeni; nayo yonke eliliva nizibekelele yona ize igcinwe kude kuse. 24. baza bayibeka kwada kwasa njengokuba ebeyalele u-Mosese, ayanuka ke akwabiko mpetu kuyo kanjalo. 25. wandula wati uMosese yityani leyo namhlanje ngokuba namhla yisabata ku-Yehova, aniyi kuyifumana ezindle namhla. 26. noyibuta imihla ibe mitandatu kodwa ngomhla wesixenxe ngowesabata ayiyi kubako ngawo. 27. kwaza kwati ngomhla wesixenxe kwapuma inxenye yabantu ukuya kubuta koko bengafumananga. 28. waza wati u-Yehova ku-Mosese niyakwala kude kube nini na ukugcina imiyalelo yam nemiteto yam. 29. niyabona ke, ngokokuba u-Yehova enipile isabata, kukona anipayo ngomhla wesitandatu, isonka semihla mibini, hlalani abanye ngabanye ezindaweni zabo kungesuki namnye endaweni yake ngomhla wesixenxe. 6. hezekile 20:12 kanjalo nesabata zam ndazinika kubo ukuba zibe ngumqondiso pakati kwam nabo ukuze bakwazi okokuba mna ndinguYehova obangcwalisayo. 7. hezekile 20:20 nesabata zam nizenze ngcwele zize zibe ngumqondiso pakati kwam nani ukuze nikwazi okokuba mna Yehova ndingu-Tixo wenu. 8. kesodus 20:8-11 kumbula umhla wesabata ukuba uwenze ngcwele. 9. wosebenza imihla ibemitandatu uwenze wonke umsebenzi wako. 10. kodwa umhla wesixenxe uyisabata kuyehova utixo wako, akuyi kwenza namnye umsebenzi ngawo, kwa wena nonyana wako, nentombi yako, nesicaka sako, nesicakakazi sako, nenkomo zako, nowasemzini wako opakati kwamasango ako. 11. ngokuba ngemihla mitandatu wenza uYehova izulu nomhlaba nolwandle, nako konke okukuzo waza wapumla ngomhla wesixenxe ngoko wawutamsanqelisa uYehova umhla wesixenxe wawenza ngcwele.",
  "1. abibe (april) kesodus 13:4 namhla nje napuma ke ngenyanga engu-abibe. 2. zive (may) i kumkani 6:1 kwaza kwati ngowamakulu mane anamashumi asibozo umnyaka emva kokupuma kosapo luka-sirayeli elizweni le-jipete, ngomnyaka wesine wobukumkani buka-solomoni pezu kwo-sirayeli ngenyanga yo-zive eyiyo inyanga yesibini, waqala ukwaka indlu ka-Yehova. 3. sivane (june) estere 8:9 kwandula kwabizwa ababhali bokumkani ngexesha elo, ngenyanga yesitatu ekwa yinyanga yo-sivane ngowashumi mabini anesitatu umhla wayo kwaza kwabhalwa ngako konke wakuyalelayo u-modekai kuma-juda, nakuzo inkosi ezinkulu, neenkosi, nabapati bamazwana atabata e-yindiya kude kwase-tiyopiya, amazwana alikulu linamashumi mabini anesixenxe, izwana ngezwana njengokubala kwalo, nabantu ngabantu njengenteto yabo, nakuwo ama-juda njengokubala kwawo nanje ngenteto yawo. 4. tamuz (july) zekariya 8:19 utsho u-Yehova wemikosi ukuti: inzilo yeyesine inyanga, nenzilo yeyesihlanu, nenzilo yeyesixenxe, nenzilo yeyeshumi, zoba luvuyo nomgcobo kwindlu ka-juda kwa imitendeleko ecwayitileyo, kodwa tandani inyaniso noxolo. 5. abu (august) ezera 7:9 ngokuba ngowesinye umhla wenyanga yokuqala, bekuqalwa ukunyukwa e-babilone, nangowesinye umhla wenyanga yesihlanu, wafika e-yerusalem njengokuba isandla esilungileyo so-tixo wake sibe sipezu kwake. 6. elule (september) nehemiya 6:15 kwada kwafezwa udonga ngowamashumi mabini anesihlanu umhla wenyanga kuyo imihla imashumi mahlanu anamabini. 7.  etanime (october) i kumkani 8:2 aza onke amadoda akwa-sirayeli ahlanganiselwa kukumkani u-solomone ngeyanga yo-etanime, emtendelekweni, yona yinyanga yesixenxe. 8.  bule (november) i kumkani 6:38 nangomnyaka weshumi linesinye ngenyanga yo-bule eyinyanga yesibozo ibigqitywa leyondlu ngazo zonke indawo zayo, nangaso sonke isimilo sayo, kwanjalo ebeyaka iminyaka yasixenxe. 9.  kislev (december) nehemiya 1:1-3 amazwi kanehemiya unyana ka-Hakaliya, kwaye kute ngenyanga yo-kislev, ngomnyakawamashumi mabini, xa bendiko eshushane komkulu. 2. kwafika uhanani, omnye kubazalwana bam, yena namadoda atile akwa-juda, ndaza ndababuza ngama-juda abesindile, lawo abesele kubatinjwa, nange-yerusalem. 3. baye besiti kum abaseleyo, abo basele kubatinjwa kona elizwananeni baseshweni elikulu nasekudelekeni, kanjalo udonga lwe-yerusalem lucitiwe, namasango ayo atshisiwe ngomlilo. 10. tibete (january) estere 2:16 kwanjalo u-estere wasiwa kukumkani uhasheveroshe, endlwini yake yobukumkani, ngenyanga yeshumi, eyinyanga yo-tibete, ngowesixenxe umnyaka wobumkani bake. 11. shebate (february) zekariya ngowamashumi mabini anesine umhla wenyanga yeshumi linesinye, eyinyanga yo-shebate, ngowesibini umnyaka ka-dariyusi, leza ilizwi lika-yehova ku-zekariya unyana ka-berekiya, unyana ka-hido, umprofite lisiti. 12. adare (march) estere 3:7 ngenyanga yokuqala ekwa yinyanga yo-nisane, ngoweshumi elinesibini umnyaka wokumkani u-hasheveroshe, kwawiswa iPuri (oko kukuti iqashiso) ebusweni buka-hamani, kwimini ngemini, nakwinyanga ngenyanga, kwada kwakuyo eyeshumi elinesibini inyanga, ekwa yinyanga yo-adare.",
  "Izizukulvvana luke 3:23-38 waye yena u-yesu wayeyiminyaka engati ngamashumi matatu ubudala bake akuqala ukufundisa, enguye (njengokuba kusitiwa) unyana ka-josefe, obengoka-heli. 24. obengoka- matati, obengoka-levi, obengoka-maleki, obengoka-jana, obengoka-josefe. 25. obengoka- matatiya, obengoka-amotse, obengoka-nahume, obengoka-esili, obengoka-nagayi. 26. obengo- mahati, obengoka-matitiya, obengoka-shimehi, obengoka-josefe, obengoka-juda. 27. obengoka johanane, obengoka-resa, obengoka-zerubabeli, obengoka-shalatiyeli, obengoka-neri. 28. obengoka-maleki, obengoka-adi, obengoka-kosame, obengoka-elimodame, obengoka-here. 29. obengoka-jose, obengoka-eliyezeri, obengoka-yorime, obengoka-matati, obengoka-levi. 30. obengoka-simone, obengoka-jude, obengoka-josefe, obengoka-johane, obengoka-eliyakime. 31. obengoka-meleya, obengoka-menane, obengoka-matata, obengoka-natane, obengoka- davide. 32. obengoka-jese, obengoka-obedi, obengoka-bohazi, obengoka-salimone, obengoka-nahashone. 33. obengoka-haminadabi, obengoka-rame, obengoka-hetserone, obengoka-faretse, obengoka-juda. 34. obengoka-yakobi, obengoka-yisake, obengoka- abrahame, obengoka-tera, obengoka-nahore. 35. obengoka-seruge, obengoka-rehu, obengoka-pelege, obengoka-hebere, obengoka-sala. obengoka-kenane, obengoka-rafatsade, obengoka-sheme, obengoka-nowa, obengoka-lameki. 37. obengoka-metushela, obengoka- enoki, obengoka-yeredi, obengoka-mahalalele, obengoka-kenane. 38. obengoka-enoshe, obengoka-shete, obengoka-adame, obengoka-Tixo.",
  "lntombi zase-yerusalem zothi zime ziphahle umnyango udade rarele no-leya bame bona ude udlule umkhumbi, u-bawo abraham no-masara balandele ngemva, u-malusi akhokele. umhlambi wobe uvuma lo mbongo - yizani kum nonke. kumiwa ngenyawo kuvunywe umbongo kuthandazwe mateyu 6:9-13, ibe ngumbongo kuleswe maculo 39:1-13 kulandele izithethi. .3.kugqibeleni kuleswa i makorinte 15:40-58 ibe yintshumayelo. umngcelele ukuya emangcwabeni kukhokela abefundisi be-bandla lika-Thixo nee-ngcwele zika-kristu okanye u-malusi; u-rarele no- leya baphahle umkhumbi. u-bawo abraham no-masara balandele emva komkhumbi, emva koko ababujelwa, kuze i-kwayara ngabane ngabane amadoda emacaleni ivuma - bona ke uyeza namafu. xa kusondelwa emafihlweni iyakuyeka ingoma, umalusi afunde lamazwi ngokuphakamileyo-- Ivangeli ka-johane 11-25-26. mna ndilulo uvuko ndibubo nobom okholwayo kum nakuba afayo uyakudla ubom, nosukuba edla ubom ekholwa kum akasayi kufa naphakade. amen. emangcwabeni makuvunywe umbongo kuthandazwe mateyu 6:9-13, ibe ngumbongo kuze kufundwe: job 14:1-2 umntu ozelwe ngumfazi ungomihla mifutshane nokolise ukuba nesitukutezi. 2. uyavela njengembali, andul'ukunqanyulwa, uyabaleka njengesitunzi angahlali ke. i timoti 6:7 ngokuba singangenanga nanto elizweni kusekuhleni ukuba kanjako asingephumi nanto. job 1:21 wati ndize ndapuma esizalweni sika-ma, ndize ndobuyela kona kanjalo. nguYehova obenika nguYehova ohluthileyo, igama lika-Yehova malibongwe. kuze kufundwe lamazwi: njengoko kumkholisile u-tixo ophezu konke entandweni yemvume yakhe ukususa elizweni esi sithandwa somzalwana/dade, ngoko siyawufaka umzimba wakhe emhlambeni. umhlaba emhlabeni uthuthu eluthuthuthwini uthuli eluthulini sikhangela eluvukweni ngomhla wokugqibelo nakubom belizwe elizayo ngayo inkosi uyesu ukristu oyakuza engena sono elusindisweni. Isityilo 14:13:ndaza ndeva ilizwi lisiti kum, 'bhala ukuti- banetamsanqa abafayo abefela enkosini emva koku ewe utsho umoya ukuze baphumle kuyo imizano yabo, ithi imisebenzi yabo ilandele kwanabo. kovunywa ingoma kuvalwe mateyu 6:9-13 juda 1:24-25. kwandule kufundwe inkatha nezaziso njalo-njalo, kubuyelwe ekhayeni. amen.",
];
